{"tid":1642184,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"對唔住 我放棄政府工","createTime":"2019-10-09T15:20:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T03:38:03.000Z","uid":3890,"like":8,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"b72733844b78f249f058c4dcb823abbab49dec48","tid":1642184,"uid":3890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:20:25.000Z","msg":"我係澳洲嘅大學grad 屋企係普通公屋家庭 <br />\n<br />\n父母年紀大 我之前(未有送中嘅時候)報左入境事務處助理 琴日收到通知去見 但係我本身有紋身 加上我係深黄 好多朋友叫我見左先入去做有良知嘅人 但我知有紋身都做唔到<br />\n<br />\n奈何洗紋身都貴又揾唔到信譽好嘅鋪去洗 我屋企係黃 但我仲要一個人照顧兩老 醫生錢水電煤一個月都好大開支 宜家揾18k一個月真係好吃力 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔好屌 我純粹覺得攰想講下 阻左巴打幾分鐘 唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇過來人可以分享下"},{"pid":"46a9c3e86ace048c35ef7dae9805098feaace8ef","tid":1642184,"uid":175752,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:22:55.000Z","msg":"點解我隻隻字都明 但睇唔明篇野"},{"pid":"e20723c76641cd11cabe15ef0ab5f34dda486c88","tid":1642184,"uid":207122,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"講乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f449ce34baf06372422b0c3edea5d01622fcfd24","tid":1642184,"uid":3890,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:24:33.000Z","msg":"我純粹呻下 冇乜特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b00b409dd479358158c70c569b8519dbd906a6a6","tid":1642184,"uid":97267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:25:46.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"b7a788cc59ef91bb9ba9f096e40377e2c8b81dd3","tid":1642184,"uid":212878,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:27:20.000Z","msg":"樓主智力係咪有問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed21f940410a4fb5d5450571c369239202b8de4e","tid":1642184,"uid":186811,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T15:28:45.000Z","msg